                            <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                                    <locus target="#229va"/>
                                    <note>Partly erased colophon indicating the name of
                                        the sponsor, a woman, and the church to which the manuscript belonged. All proper names have been erased. Wright describes this colophon as a later note, and while
                                    its hand seems to differ from the main hand, the careful writing and text dividers consistent with the text dividers used throughout
                                    suggest that it was part of the initial process of production.</note>
                                    ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘታቦተ፡ <del rend="erasure"/>
                                        ዘአጽሐፈታ፡ በንዋያ፡ <del rend="erasure"/> ድንግል፡ ምስለ፡
                                        ውሉዳ፡ <del rend="erasure"/>
                            </colophon>
                        </msItem>
                        
